By: Swâmi Brahmânanda
---
If a person has a sincere fervour for the Lord and is eager to follow
a spiritual path, he is sure to meet a true guru through the grace of
the Lord. Consequently, the spiritual aspirant should not be troubled
about the coming of a guru.
